	<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/gem" underlined="true">Normal Gems</style> or crafted form
	<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/exquisite_gem" underlined="true">Exquisite Gems</style>, flawless gems don't have many uses, 
